snippet.title: POPGOES Developer Commentary
snippet.description:
This is the POPGOES Developer Commentary from the POPGOES Creator Pack.

1:20 - Where did the idea of Popgoes building Blackrabbit come from?
4:15 - Development struggles and stories
6:14 - How did the transition from POPGOES 2015 to POPGOES 2016 evolve?
9:13 - Where did the concept of Strings and the Lux Animatronics come from?
15:53 - How did you think of Gem Stone and Grave Stone?
20:35 - What's your favourite part of POPGOES? Favourite plot point and plot twist?
24:00 - If you were to improve POPGOES, and were given full control, what would you do?

You can download POPGOES, POPGOES Arcade, and the POPGOES Creator Pack here: 
http://gamejolt.com/games/popgoes-official/64790

Some slight editing and quality changes were made in this video, compared to the one in the pack. 

You are free to make a "reaction video" or discussion video about this, but please do not reupload the video onto your own channel. Thanks!
